1
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:29,820
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:33,275
=Episode 16=
(After I gave my burning soul,)

3
00:00:33,337 --> 00:00:35,225
(I don't believe it bears no fruit.)

4
00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:47,440
Your love is nothing special.

5
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:50,760
Today, Zhao

6
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,960
took your child

7
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:55,000
out of fear of the Heavenly Dao.

8
00:00:55,440 --> 00:00:56,960
Tomorrow, he will

9
00:00:57,560 --> 00:01:00,000
destroy you

10
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:02,640
to save his own life.

11
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:04,720
That's impossible.

12
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,920
If Zhao does this,

13
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,560
it's for my own good.

14
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:15,120
You really are naive.

15
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:21,800
What's more important
than your own life?

16
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:24,360
Without it,

17
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:27,440
there's only endless void.

18
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:31,120
What love is there to talk about?

19
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:34,160
If this lover dies,

20
00:01:35,080 --> 00:01:37,200
just find another.

21
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,440
What's the difference?

22
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:42,320
Of course there's a difference.

23
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:46,360
Love may live in my heart,

24
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,560
but its root

25
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,360
is in him.

26
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,080
What matters is him.

27
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,800
Only him.

28
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,000
Ridiculous.

29
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,200
I don't believe

30
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:03,920
his life matters more than yours.

31
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:07,560
If you can't do it,

32
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:11,640
then let me take your body.

33
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:15,000
I'll kill him for you.

34
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,000
I'm telling you,

35
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,560
he would never hurt me.

36
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:23,200
And I won't let you hurt him.

37
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,640
How laughable.

38
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:31,200
Cutie,

39
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:34,800
let me help you.

40
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:47,400
Shut up! Get back inside!

41
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,240
We'll see about that.

42
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:05,960
Zhao!

43
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,640
Zhao!

44
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:18,800
(Baobao, your father is useless.)

45
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,880
(I couldn't find a perfect solution.)

46
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,640
(I can only seal you inside the sword.)

47
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,600
(After a hundred years,)

48
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,600
(you'll be able to take human form.)

49
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:40,520
Zhao.

50
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,200
Come, sit.

51
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:51,200
Why aren't you asleep yet?

52
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,640
Did you have a nightmare?

53
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,640
I'm used to you being by my side.

54
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,040
Without you,

55
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:02,600
I can't sleep.

56
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,200
She really likes you.

57
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:20,920
Hello.

58
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:21,920
My name is He Xi.

59
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:15,160
Zhao,

60
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:22,720
I want to become one with you,

61
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,800
never to be apart.

62
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,160
I know.

63
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:33,280
Nothing can separate us.

64
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:42,920
- Xi.
- Zhao.

65
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,600
You go first.

66
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,360
I...

67
00:05:49,350 --> 00:05:51,280
I may need to return
to the God Realm for a few days.

68
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,560
Don't blow the whistle to call me.

69
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,640
I'll be back in about a month.

70
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,720
I was just about to say,

71
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,360
every year on the 15th
of the first month,

72
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:04,280
I go up the mountain to gather ginseng.

73
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:06,640
If you come back and don't see me,

74
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,960
I'll be in the mountains.

75
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:11,720
Wait a few days. I'll be back.

76
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,480
But...

77
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,960
Don't worry.

78
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:19,400
That mountain is as familiar to me

79
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,040
as Baihua Hall.

80
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,960
Have you lost your mind?

81
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:09,280
Are you trying to dig me out?

82
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,040
Don't even think about it.

83
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,280
If you dig me out,

84
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,720
you won't survive either.

85
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:21,160
We are one body.

86
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,920
Why destroy each other?

87
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:27,280
Don't you understand

88
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,920
you should love yourself first?

89
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,400
Heavenly Dao!

90
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,400
Show yourself!

91
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,600
(Have you taken that abomination?)

92
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:38,720
I have.

93
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:41,720
(The love between a god
and a demon defies the Heavenly Dao.)

94
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:44,040
(You two nearly caused a catastrophe.)

95
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,200
(Go destroy the demon,)

96
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:47,400
(or you'll both
suffer heavenly lightning.)

97
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,960
That's none of your concern.

98
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,400
As long as I strip away the demon heart,

99
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,600
I'll be free from your control.

100
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,280
By then...

101
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:55,840
Sister, no!

102
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,560
Even the Heavenly Dao
won't be able to trouble me anymore.

103
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,080
No!

104
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,960
You've lost your mind!

105
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,280
My dear sister,

106
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:06,520
I believe in your love with him.

107
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:08,600
But listen to me.

108
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,480
It's not worth it

109
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:11,920
for a man.

110
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,920
It's not worth it!

111
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,360
It really isn't!

112
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:16,720
Today,

113
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:19,640
I'll show you

114
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:22,400
what this worthless love in your eyes

115
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:25,040
really looks like!

116
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,520
This love

117
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,520
will reveal itself!

118
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,520
Zhao...

119
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:12,920
It worked...

120
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:18,160
Xi and I truly love each other.

121
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,920
I will bear
all the lightning punishment alone.

122
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,280
Just spare Xi.

123
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:26,800
(Arrogant and ignorant.)

124
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,800
(Does it hurt?)

125
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:31,440
It hurts.

126
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:33,280
(Will you change?)

127
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,040
No.

128
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:36,800
(Will you change or not?)

129
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:37,560
No!

130
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,640
(Will you change or not?)

131
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:39,440
No!

132
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:40,520
(Will you change or not?)

133
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:42,160
No! No!

134
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,320
No!

135
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:56,880
Even in pain, I won't change.

136
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,120
Even in death, I won't change.

137
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:00,640
Never, for all eternity!

138
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:28,800
(Do you regret it?)

139
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:31,920
No.

140
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,760
(For a demon,)

141
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,280
(is it worth it?)

142
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:38,440
After meeting Xi,

143
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:40,040
I realized

144
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,920
gods

145
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:46,400
are incomplete

146
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,800
and lonely.

147
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:52,280
You can tell me she's a demon,

148
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:58,280
that she'll bring chaos to the world,

149
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:04,160
that her existence
goes against the gods.

150
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:05,920
But none of that

151
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,800
can kill

152
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,920
my love for her.

153
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:23,320
I will love her.

154
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:27,120
Forever.

155
00:11:28,162 --> 00:11:29,642
(Stubborn fool.)

156
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:32,280
(Even if you
take her lightning punishment,)

157
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:34,280
(I still won't spare her)

158
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:36,880
(for your divine future.)

159
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,800
If being a god

160
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:46,000
means I can't be with her,

161
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,680
then I

162
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,400
don't want to be a god.

163
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:22,760
I'll return

164
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:26,520
my divine heart to you!

165
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:29,400
(For a demon,)

166
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:33,120
(you gave up a divine heart
cultivated for a thousand years.)

167
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:34,920
(Was it worth it?)

168
00:12:39,040 --> 00:12:40,000
It was.

169
00:12:51,712 --> 00:12:56,712
♪When starlight cuts
through the long night♪

170
00:12:57,250 --> 00:12:58,010
(Zhao...)

171
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:00,320
(Zhao...)

172
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:04,512
♪It bids farewell to another blue sky♪

173
00:13:05,212 --> 00:13:07,137
♪To meet is to overlap♪

174
00:13:07,187 --> 00:13:09,112
♪To see is to part again♪

175
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,775
(Xi...)

176
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:11,120
(Xi...)

177
00:13:12,300 --> 00:13:18,987
♪Counting every moment,
unwilling to pause♪

178
00:13:20,787 --> 00:13:25,637
♪As raindrops kiss the ground♪

179
00:13:27,987 --> 00:13:32,925
♪Soaking these hazy, drowsy eyes♪

180
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:36,462
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

181
00:13:36,512 --> 00:13:38,262
♪Chasing something always out of reach♪

182
00:13:38,262 --> 00:13:41,100
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

183
00:13:41,162 --> 00:13:47,687
♪Living the same day
over and over again♪

184
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:52,700
♪Too bad the rain will stop, the wind
will fade, tomorrow will clear♪

185
00:13:52,775 --> 00:13:55,412
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

186
00:13:55,537 --> 00:14:02,600
♪Let the long shadows
whisper what's in your heart♪♪

187
00:14:02,812 --> 00:14:07,200
♪If in a dream, I can hear your voice♪

188
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:10,000
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

189
00:14:10,087 --> 00:14:17,287
♪Let it be us drawing endlessly close♪

190
00:14:32,762 --> 00:14:37,362
♪Too bad the rain will stop, the wind
will fade, tomorrow will clear♪

191
00:14:37,475 --> 00:14:40,100
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

192
00:14:40,175 --> 00:14:47,300
♪Not even in time,
to tell you how I feel♪

193
00:14:47,512 --> 00:14:49,052
♪If the rain won't stop♪

194
00:14:49,052 --> 00:14:51,802
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

195
00:14:51,802 --> 00:14:54,772
♪Let love go on♪

196
00:14:54,772 --> 00:14:57,322
♪Until forever♪

197
00:14:57,322 --> 00:15:01,652
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
